45
00:06:45,460 --> 00:06:46,950
They only needed 50,000 yuan more.

46
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:48,630
Zhou Jian was rich.

47
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,230
The traffic police also said

48
00:06:50,230 --> 00:06:51,690
