183
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:32,510
as a murderer.

184
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:34,770
You lived every day as if it was your last.

185
00:14:34,990 --> 00:14:36,790
In order to repay Chen Jingming,

186
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:38,460
