195
00:14:51,310 --> 00:14:52,670
But you didn't expect

196
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:54,400
that we could do a DNA test

197
00:14:54,400 --> 00:14:55,680
on a burnt corpse.

198
00:14:59,870 --> 00:15:00,750
Huang Bingde,

199
00:15:01,060 --> 00:15:02,410
