285
00:20:12,230 --> 00:20:13,030
That's right.

286
00:20:13,410 --> 00:20:14,670
Lei Naiwu was thinking

287
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:16,600
that he could find Chen Jingming

288
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:17,850
after being released

